=Tears In Heaven=

15
00:01:26,472 --> 00:01:28,968
=Episode 21=

16
00:01:34,759 --> 00:01:35,320
Mr. Lin.

17
00:01:36,080 --> 00:01:38,360
Lei Yuzheng had quite a fall this time.

18
00:01:38,839 --> 00:01:41,520
It'll take a while for him
to make a comeback.

19
00:01:42,800 --> 00:01:44,080
I didn't expect that.

20
00:01:44,679 --> 00:01:45,559
I…

21
00:01:45,919 --> 00:01:47,279
What didn't you expect?

22
00:01:50,360 --> 00:01:51,240
Nothing.

23
00:01:52,880 --> 00:01:56,320
Mr. Lin, it's good that
Lei Yuzheng is gone now.

24
00:01:56,639 --> 00:01:58,320
Why do you still seem
to worry a lot?

25
00:01:58,600 --> 00:02:00,559
You can take this chance
to get promoted, right?

26
00:02:00,880 --> 00:02:01,839
Promoted?

27
00:02:03,800 --> 00:02:05,759
I, Lin Xiangyuan, will never
take advantage of other people.

28
00:02:06,600 --> 00:02:08,839
I was gonna fight with
Lei Yuzheng face to face.

29
00:02:09,440 --> 00:02:10,520
If I win then,

30
00:02:10,759 --> 00:02:12,279
it means that
I am really more capable than him.

31
00:02:13,440 --> 00:02:15,800
But the result means everything.

32
00:02:16,119 --> 00:02:17,919
As long as you become
the president of Yutian,

33
00:02:18,199 --> 00:02:20,080
no one cares about
what means you took.

34
00:02:21,240 --> 00:02:23,119
They will all look up to you.

35
00:02:33,000 --> 00:02:33,800
Xieli,

36
00:02:34,759 --> 00:02:37,839
what do you think
Lei Yuzheng is doing right now?

37
00:02:37,960 --> 00:02:39,199
What else can he do?

38
00:02:40,800 --> 00:02:42,839
He must be crying out loud at the court.

39
00:02:43,880 --> 00:02:46,279
Now, the old is in hospital,

40
00:02:46,520 --> 00:02:47,919
and the young is in jail.

41
00:02:48,320 --> 00:02:51,000
Now it's time for you, Mr. Lin,
to take charge.

42
00:02:56,639 --> 00:02:58,880
Mr. Jiang, directors are waiting for you
to join the meeting.

43
00:03:01,199 --> 00:03:05,440
Look at this,
these reporters are going way too far.

44
00:03:06,240 --> 00:03:08,360
They used such title as
"Yutian's stock market scandal" and

45
00:03:08,679 --> 00:03:10,679
"Construction of Entertainment Center
project might be called off".

46
00:03:11,160 --> 00:03:12,679
They are talking nonsense.

47
00:03:14,360 --> 00:03:17,039
Mr. Jiang,
that's what reporters usually do.

48
00:03:17,279 --> 00:03:18,360
As long as they can make
a big news out of something,

49
00:03:18,479 --> 00:03:20,000
they would exaggerate everything.

50
00:03:20,119 --> 00:03:21,440
Speaking of that,

51
00:03:21,600 --> 00:03:23,039
not only those reporters,

52
00:03:24,039 --> 00:03:25,839
but also our employees are

53
00:03:26,160 --> 00:03:26,880
talking about rumors right now.

54
00:03:27,919 --> 00:03:28,839
What do you mean?

55
00:03:30,600 --> 00:03:31,720
They are all saying that

56
00:03:32,160 --> 00:03:34,119
it will take a while for Lei Yuzheng
to make a comeback.

57
00:03:34,279 --> 00:03:35,960
And if no one takes the lead right now,

58
00:03:36,360 --> 00:03:38,000
the Entertainment Center project
will be affected.

59
00:03:38,360 --> 00:03:39,240
Mr. Jiang,

60
00:03:40,279 --> 00:03:42,359
everyone is waiting for you
to take the lead.

61
00:03:45,279 --> 00:03:46,760
But I don't know much about

62
00:03:47,640 --> 00:03:49,760
the Entertainment City project.

63
00:03:50,239 --> 00:03:51,559
If I take over right now,

64
00:03:51,920 --> 00:03:53,399
isn't it too hasty?

65
00:03:54,040 --> 00:03:55,079
I might trap myself

66
00:03:55,559 --> 00:03:58,440
later on.

67
00:04:00,880 --> 00:04:01,880
By the way, Mr. Jiang,

68
00:04:02,480 --> 00:04:04,079
is Fanlv feeling better?

69
00:04:04,440 --> 00:04:05,559
How's her appetite?

70
00:04:05,839 --> 00:04:07,679
I'm planning to go back to my hometown,

71
00:04:07,920 --> 00:04:09,279
and bring some delicacies
for her to improve her health.

72
00:04:10,559 --> 00:04:11,679
Fanlv is fine.

73
00:04:12,160 --> 00:04:14,279
Xiangyuan, you are very thoughtful.

74
00:04:17,079 --> 00:04:19,920
Ah, regarding the
Entertainment Center project,

75
00:04:20,239 --> 00:04:22,880
you know it the best
besides Lei Yuzheng.

76
00:04:24,839 --> 00:04:26,920
Come and join the meeting with me.

77
00:04:39,000 --> 00:04:40,799
Lin, have a seat.

78
00:04:51,720 --> 00:04:53,480
Regarding what happened to
Yutian recently,

79
00:04:54,200 --> 00:04:55,959
I don't have to recap it.

80
00:04:56,480 --> 00:04:59,000
Why don't all of you

81
00:04:59,279 --> 00:05:00,679
contribute your ideas?

82
00:05:02,160 --> 00:05:03,279
Such a big company

83
00:05:03,480 --> 00:05:05,720
needs a leader.

84
00:05:05,839 --> 00:05:08,720
Jiang, you should think of a way.

85
00:05:11,519 --> 00:05:12,600
Yuzheng is in trouble,

86
00:05:13,559 --> 00:05:15,320
and brother Ting is in the hospital.

87
00:05:15,480 --> 00:05:17,559
Everyone must be very anxious.

88
00:05:18,160 --> 00:05:19,760
But it's still important

89
00:05:20,079 --> 00:05:23,079
to maintain the order
within the company.

90
00:05:23,880 --> 00:05:25,480
Why don't we vote by raising hands

91
00:05:26,119 --> 00:05:28,920
to elect a temporary president
to take charge for now?

92
00:05:29,839 --> 00:05:30,679
How does that sound?

93
00:05:31,000 --> 00:05:32,600
As far as I'm concerned,
we can skip that step.

94
00:05:32,799 --> 00:05:34,440
The one who can take charge
is you, Mr. Jiang.

95
00:05:34,640 --> 00:05:35,720
You should take this position.

96
00:05:36,279 --> 00:05:37,000
Me?

97
00:05:38,000 --> 00:05:40,119
No, no, no. How could it be me?

98
00:05:41,279 --> 00:05:42,559
Don't be modest.

99
00:05:42,920 --> 00:05:45,920
The Entertainment Center project
belonged to Xinsheng in the first place.

100
00:05:46,079 --> 00:05:48,640
Although Yutian is in charge of
the development,

101
00:05:48,799 --> 00:05:50,079
you also have the responsibility.

102
00:05:50,640 --> 00:05:52,239
Mr. Jiang, don't be so modest.

103
00:05:52,640 --> 00:05:53,920
Mr. Jiang, you should take it.

104
00:05:54,040 --> 00:05:55,160
Mr. Jiang, I will vote for you.

105
00:05:55,239 --> 00:05:55,679
I agree.

106
00:05:55,839 --> 00:05:56,679
Yes, I agree.

107
00:05:57,839 --> 00:06:00,040
All right. Since everyone has
such high expectation in me,

108
00:06:01,799 --> 00:06:04,160
and we should take the overall interests
of the company into account.

109
00:06:04,799 --> 00:06:08,399
I will just take this position for now,

110
00:06:08,720 --> 00:06:10,920
and hope everyone could understand.

111
00:06:11,119 --> 00:06:13,000
Of course.

112
00:06:13,839 --> 00:06:18,720
But a leader cannot fight by oneself.

113
00:06:19,239 --> 00:06:21,480
It's not enough to do it all

114
00:06:21,600 --> 00:06:23,119
by myself.

115
00:06:24,760 --> 00:06:28,119
Lin has been my assistant
for so many years.

116
00:06:28,600 --> 00:06:31,160
We've built great rapport
with each other.

117
00:06:31,480 --> 00:06:32,920
Everyone here has witnessed

118
00:06:33,119 --> 00:06:35,320
his ability.

119
00:06:35,480 --> 00:06:38,079
So I suggest that I will supervise

120
00:06:38,279 --> 00:06:40,880
the Entertainment Center project,
and Lin will be in charge.

121
00:06:47,640 --> 00:06:50,959
I know that Lin is my future son-in-law,

122
00:06:51,239 --> 00:06:53,799
and I should have left him out of this,
so that people won't gossip about it.

123
00:06:54,119 --> 00:06:57,679
But to the benefit of Yutian
and the Entertainment Center project,

124
00:06:57,920 --> 00:07:01,000
I think we can entrust Lin
with this task.

125
00:07:01,480 --> 00:07:04,640
Lin, the investment that
you were working on

126
00:07:05,000 --> 00:07:06,160
is still possible, right?

127
00:07:06,519 --> 00:07:08,760
I'll keep working on it.
I think it is possible for us to get it.

128
00:07:10,600 --> 00:07:13,920
If Lin can collect money
for the Entertainment Center project,

129
00:07:14,119 --> 00:07:15,959
he will be the hero of Yutian.

130
00:07:16,239 --> 00:07:17,959
We can't even thank him enough.

131
00:07:23,640 --> 00:07:24,640
Everyone,

132
00:07:25,760 --> 00:07:27,279
at the very beginning,
Xinsheng cooperated with Yutian

133
00:07:27,519 --> 00:07:30,160
on the Entertainment Center project
by offering it as a gift.

134
00:07:30,720 --> 00:07:32,119
Since the board has decided

135
00:07:32,519 --> 00:07:33,959
that I will take charge of this project,

136
00:07:34,119 --> 00:07:35,760
I know how much responsibility I have.

137
00:07:36,000 --> 00:07:37,920
I won't let anyone down.

138
00:07:51,020 --> 00:07:53,239
(Police)

139
00:07:59,839 --> 00:08:01,599
(Jiangkan Detention Center)

140
00:08:03,039 --> 00:08:03,799
Get off the car.

141
00:08:08,199 --> 00:08:09,579
(Jiangkan Detention Center)

142
00:08:16,679 --> 00:08:18,760
According to Article 180

143
00:08:18,760 --> 00:08:20,400
of the Criminal Law
of the People’s Republic of China,

144
00:08:20,719 --> 00:08:24,280
the defendant Lei Yuzheng,
the prior president of Yutian,

145
00:08:24,520 --> 00:08:26,200
is sentenced for 8-month detention
(Jiangkan Detention Center)

146
00:08:26,359 --> 00:08:27,880
due to the charge of
disclosing confidential information,

147
00:08:28,440 --> 00:08:29,760
and immediate execution is required.

148
00:08:31,860 --> 00:08:34,499
(Silence)

149
00:08:38,599 --> 00:08:39,880
Time is like a one-way road.

150
00:08:41,119 --> 00:08:42,559
You can only move forward
without going back.

151
00:08:43,559 --> 00:08:45,239
There's no pure luck in this world.

152
00:08:45,799 --> 00:08:48,960
Everyone needs to pay the price
for their mistakes.

153
00:08:52,520 --> 00:08:53,400
Go inside.

154
00:09:41,359 --> 00:09:42,280
My name is Liu Siyang.

155
00:09:44,280 --> 00:09:45,479
It must be the first time for you.

156
00:09:46,039 --> 00:09:47,000
I can tell that
you're not used to here yet.

157
00:09:53,359 --> 00:09:54,679
It will be better in a few days.

158
00:10:14,599 --> 00:10:15,559
Here you are.

159
00:10:17,039 --> 00:10:19,400
Xiaosu, it was on TV.

160
00:10:19,719 --> 00:10:21,440
Did Lei Yuzheng actually go to jail?

161
00:10:25,840 --> 00:10:27,239
I couldn't do anything about it.

162
00:10:27,440 --> 00:10:29,200
There was no evidence and

163
00:10:29,320 --> 00:10:31,320
nothing was beneficial towards him.

164
00:10:32,159 --> 00:10:33,880
He also didn't want to explain about it,

165
00:10:35,000 --> 00:10:37,239
and took all the responsibilities
by himself.

166
00:10:37,640 --> 00:10:38,679
So,

167
00:10:39,919 --> 00:10:42,159
I couldn't do anything
but watching him get accused.

168
00:10:44,440 --> 00:10:45,799
It's all my fault.

169
00:10:46,280 --> 00:10:47,760
I couldn't do anything.

170
00:10:49,000 --> 00:10:50,479
I couldn't help him.

171
00:10:51,239 --> 00:10:52,599
What happened to Lei Yuzheng this time

172
00:10:52,640 --> 00:10:54,520
is really a big issue.

173
00:10:55,000 --> 00:10:56,159
Since when...

174
00:11:01,239 --> 00:11:02,119
Siqi,

175
00:11:06,559 --> 00:11:07,719
Let's break up.

176
00:11:11,679 --> 00:11:12,679
What did you say?

177
00:11:13,440 --> 00:11:14,559
Mr. Lei went to jail,

178
00:11:16,760 --> 00:11:18,080
and the chairman is in a coma.

179
00:11:20,239 --> 00:11:21,880
It's all because of me.

180
00:11:23,479 --> 00:11:24,719
Since the past cannot be changed,

181
00:11:25,520 --> 00:11:26,799
I cannot just sit here and

182
00:11:26,919 --> 00:11:28,880
have date with you.

183
00:11:30,719 --> 00:11:33,119
He Qunfei, what is wrong with you?

184
00:11:34,159 --> 00:11:35,559
Don't regret if you say this.

185
00:11:35,760 --> 00:11:37,159
There's nothing to regret.

186
00:11:38,520 --> 00:11:40,080
Things are already this bad.

187
00:11:41,559 --> 00:11:43,479
I deserve whatever it costs.

188
00:11:44,840 --> 00:11:45,960
He Qunfei, don't be so impulsive.

189
00:11:46,039 --> 00:11:47,159
You can leave this behind.

190
00:11:48,599 --> 00:11:49,640
He Qunfei,

191
00:11:50,640 --> 00:11:51,799
you wanna break up, right?

192
00:11:53,400 --> 00:11:55,440
From now on, let's go our own ways.

193
00:11:55,599 --> 00:11:56,799
Don't you dare regret it.

194
00:11:57,000 --> 00:11:57,320
Siqi.

195
00:11:57,479 --> 00:11:59,000
He Qunfei, get out of here now.

196
00:11:59,200 --> 00:12:00,359
Now.

197
00:12:00,719 --> 00:12:02,359
Siqi, calm down.

198
00:12:04,039 --> 00:12:04,960
Xiaosu.

199
00:12:05,760 --> 00:12:07,440
I really appreciate your help
this whole time.

200
00:12:08,520 --> 00:12:09,599
See you.

201
00:12:22,840 --> 00:12:24,840
What are you two doing?

202
00:12:57,880 --> 00:12:58,919
You can't fall asleep, right?

203
00:13:00,080 --> 00:13:01,880
There're only two of us

204
00:13:02,760 --> 00:13:04,039
in this 9-square meter room.

205
00:13:04,479 --> 00:13:06,159
If you keep silent like this,

206
00:13:07,000 --> 00:13:08,039
it won't be long till

207
00:13:08,559 --> 00:13:09,840
we both got crazy.

208
00:13:23,719 --> 00:13:24,919
You seem to be

209
00:13:25,799 --> 00:13:27,320
someone who has power,

210
00:13:28,400 --> 00:13:30,080
and can't bear with living in jail.

211
00:13:30,919 --> 00:13:31,960
No wonder.

212
00:13:32,880 --> 00:13:34,080
Rich people,

213
00:13:45,919 --> 00:13:47,080
who's like you,

214
00:13:48,640 --> 00:13:50,880
always seem proud when nothing happens.

215
00:13:51,599 --> 00:13:53,239
As long as they get troubled,

216
00:13:53,520 --> 00:13:56,559
they will look hopeless.

217
00:13:57,159 --> 00:13:59,159
I look down on people like you.

218
00:14:00,760 --> 00:14:01,880
What did you say?

219
00:14:02,760 --> 00:14:04,239
Nothing.

220
00:14:04,479 --> 00:14:06,200
I don't have respect
for people like you.

221
00:14:06,320 --> 00:14:07,440
Why?

222
00:14:10,760 --> 00:14:12,000
Too weak.

223
00:14:14,520 --> 00:14:15,559
You hit me?

224
00:14:17,080 --> 00:14:18,799
Hit me! Come, hit me!

225
00:14:20,479 --> 00:14:21,359
Hit me!

226
00:14:26,239 --> 00:14:26,799
Hit me!

227
00:14:27,559 --> 00:14:28,119
Stop it!

228
00:14:29,400 --> 00:14:30,159
Do it!

229
00:14:30,719 --> 00:14:31,440
What are you doing?

230
00:14:31,599 --> 00:14:32,599
What are you doing?

231
00:14:34,000 --> 00:14:34,840
Stand aside.

232
00:14:36,799 --> 00:14:37,880
Who started first?

233
00:14:43,440 --> 00:14:44,119
Xiangyuan,

234
00:14:44,760 --> 00:14:46,159
was what Fanlv said true?

235
00:14:47,239 --> 00:14:50,159
Did He Qunfei really fight with you?

236
00:14:50,919 --> 00:14:51,640
Yes.

237
00:14:52,159 --> 00:14:53,200
So, you do have something to do

238
00:14:53,640 --> 00:14:56,719
with Lei Yuzheng's trouble?

239
00:14:57,760 --> 00:14:59,919
Mr. Jiang, I've been serving you
for such a long time.

240
00:14:59,919 --> 00:15:01,400
How could you not trust me?

241
00:15:02,119 --> 00:15:03,239
How could I possibly do such

242
00:15:03,239 --> 00:15:04,640
disgraceful thing?

243
00:15:05,919 --> 00:15:06,559
Yes.

244
00:15:07,039 --> 00:15:09,000
He Qunfei fought with me
because of Lei Yuzheng.

245
00:15:09,400 --> 00:15:11,119
But it was because
he cares about Lei Yuzheng so much

246
00:15:11,559 --> 00:15:12,919
that he lost his mind.

247
00:15:13,640 --> 00:15:15,840
He's been thinking of me
as Lei Yuzheng's enemy,

248
00:15:16,840 --> 00:15:18,080
and always suspecting me.

249
00:15:19,880 --> 00:15:20,960
But I can understand that,

250
00:15:21,359 --> 00:15:22,880
because I was sent by Xinsheng anyway,

251
00:15:23,719 --> 00:15:25,000
and I don't have a direct relationship
with Lei Yuzheng.

252
00:15:25,159 --> 00:15:26,280
What do you mean by that?

253
00:15:27,000 --> 00:15:29,559
It was my decision to send you to Yutian

254
00:15:29,679 --> 00:15:31,200
for the Entertainment Center project.

255
00:15:32,359 --> 00:15:35,640
If He Qunfei is opinionative towards you

256
00:15:35,840 --> 00:15:37,039
just because of this,

257
00:15:37,159 --> 00:15:38,880
he's really shortsighted.

258
00:15:39,000 --> 00:15:40,559
You don't have to care about him.

259
00:15:41,000 --> 00:15:41,719
Sure.

260
00:15:42,280 --> 00:15:44,119
I will keep it in mind.

261
00:15:44,960 --> 00:15:47,599
Dad, do you think it's that simple?

262
00:15:48,440 --> 00:15:49,400
Fanlv,

263
00:15:50,599 --> 00:15:51,799
do you think I can actually do

264
00:15:51,880 --> 00:15:53,440
anything that hurts Lei Yuzheng?

265
00:15:54,359 --> 00:15:55,320
Do I seem like a cunning person

266
00:15:55,760 --> 00:15:57,119
to you?

267
00:15:59,200 --> 00:16:00,960
I've never been fussy with you.

268
00:16:03,000 --> 00:16:04,080
You loved Lei Yuzheng,

269
00:16:05,039 --> 00:16:06,719
