555
00:33:16,239 --> 00:33:18,439
your fame or social status?

556
00:33:19,239 --> 00:33:20,079
Mr. Lei.

557
00:33:20,599 --> 00:33:23,119
Xiaosu has been really
worried about you.

558
00:33:23,959 --> 00:33:25,199
You didn't know it but

559
00:33:25,920 --> 00:33:27,800
