564
00:33:39,239 --> 00:33:41,000
Didn't you want to see me as a loser?

565
00:33:42,280 --> 00:33:44,159
Watching a person who used to be proud

566
00:33:44,360 --> 00:33:45,919
to fall to the bottom

567
00:33:46,280 --> 00:33:47,679
like me

568
00:33:48,520 --> 00:33:49,840
can satisfy your curiosity

569
00:33:49,840 --> 00:33:51,280
and compassion, right?

570
00:33:51,719 --> 00:33:53,719
I know what you are thinking.

571
00:33:54,239 --> 00:33:56,040
The once extremely arrogant Lei Yuzheng

572
00:33:57,159 --> 00:33:58,520
is no different than other people

573
00:33:58,560 --> 00:34:00,360
when he has lost everything.

574
00:34:00,760 --> 00:34:04,040
Maybe even worse than other people,

575
00:34:04,239 --> 00:34:05,479
isn't it?

576
00:34:07,360 --> 00:34:08,120
If it can make you feel better

577
00:34:08,120 --> 00:34:10,360
to see me like this,

578
00:34:11,639 --> 00:34:12,760
